title: Mark Rothko Boxed Note Cards
description:
Send your best wishes with the beautifully reproduced artwork on these full-color full-size Mark Rothko Notecard Boxes, packaged in a large format 2 piece glossy reusable box.
  • Dimensions: 5.5 x 7.5 x 1.5 in.
  • Materials: Large-format glossy 2-piece box. Cards printed on coated paper stock
  • 20 notecards and envelopes, 4 each of 5 images.
